N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 90.4 - Fund raising professional

State Regulations

For purposes of this Chapter, fund raising professional includes professional fund
raisers, fund raising counsel, professional solicitors and commercial co-venturers, as such terms are defined in article 7-A section
171-a. Notes
